Void knight helmets are the three combat helmets used in the Void Knight equipment and Elite Void Knight equipment sets. They are rewards from the Pest Control minigame costing 200 commendation points each. There are three different kinds:

  • Void melee helm
  • Void mage helm
  • Void ranger helm

rawContent:
'''Void knight helmets''' are the three combat helmets used in the [[Void Knight equipment]] and [[Elite Void Knight equipment]] sets. They are rewards from the [[Pest Control]] [[minigame]] costing 200 [[commendation points]] each. There are three different kinds:

* [[Void melee helm]]
* [[Void mage helm]]
* [[Void ranger helm]]
